Allemande left from different formations.

sdr> /program = Program.MAINSTREAM ; setFormation(Formation.SQUARED_SET)
|      3Gv  3Bv
|
| 4B>            2G<
|
| 4G>            2B<
|
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> heads right and left thru twice
| 4B>  3Gv  3Bv  2G<
| 
| 4G>  1B^  1G^  2B<
sdr> heads face out
| 4B>  3G<  3B>  2G<
| 
| 4G>  1B<  1G>  2B<
sdr> /// easy case: allemande dancers are already facing
sdr> allemande left
| 4B<  3G>  3B<  2G>
| 
| 4G<  1B>  1G<  2B>
sdr> right and left grand ; promenade home
|      3Gv  3Bv
| 
| 4B>            2G<
| 
| 4G>            2B<
| 
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> heads right and left thru twice
| 4B>  3Gv  3Bv  2G<
| 
| 4G>  1B^  1G^  2B<
sdr> /// check that RLG chooses boy's right hand partner
sdr> right and left grand
|      1G>  1B<
| 
| 2Bv            4Gv
| 
| 2G^            4B^
| 
|      3B>  3G<
sdr> promenade home
|      3Gv  3Bv
| 
| 4B>            2G<
| 
| 4G>            2B<
| 
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> heads right and left thru twice
| 4B>  3Gv  3Bv  2G<
| 
| 4G>  1B^  1G^  2B<
sdr> /// check that allemande left chooses boy's left hand partner
sdr> allemande left
| 4B<  3G>  3B<  2G>
| 
| 4G<  1B>  1G<  2B>
sdr> right and left grand ; promenade home
|      3Gv  3Bv
| 
| 4B>            2G<
| 
| 4G>            2B<
| 
|      1B^  1G^
sdr> /exit
